      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>This collection includes a typescript of Arthur Davison
         Ficke's poem "Portrait of That Renowned Gentleman Vachel
         Lindsay as at the First Poetry Dinner He Confronted the Celtic
         Lion &amp; Bit Him in the Leg." In a letter, n.d., Ficke
         writes to Lindsay concerning the tribute he is writing about
         Lindsay.</p>
      </scopecontent>
